{
  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases a vibrant tulip in full bloom against a stark black background. The tulip is predominantly white with bold, flame-like streaks of red and yellow radiating from its center. The petals are elegantly curved, displaying a delicate texture and subtle variations in tone. The central portion of the flower is a bright, golden yellow, gradually transitioning into the white petals and then the red streaks. The lighting is dramatic, highlighting the flower's intricate details and creating strong contrasts between light and shadow. A blurred, dark red tulip is visible in the upper left corner, suggesting a field or arrangement. The image is focused on the beauty and fragility of the single tulip.",
